tex_build_master_prompt.md

# Runtime state — written by the app at boot; never belongs in version control.
# var/tex/evidence/  = the hash-chained evidence JSONL (EvidenceRecorder continues
#                      it from the file on boot; in prod it rides a persistent volume)
# var/tex/keys/      = the evidence-seal signing key, incl. PRIVATE key material
#                      (regenerated on a fresh deploy; must never be committed)
var/
# Same runtime state when the app runs with the package root (src/) as CWD. The
# bare `var/` above is root-anchored and does NOT match `src/var/`, so a second
# copy of the PRIVATE seal key + evidence chain slipped past #12.
src/var/
data/
